title: Break Your Heart* (Snippet)
lyrics:
[Snippet]
I know I've been up and down
You stuck around
Now you should leave
'Cause all I seem to do
Is break your heart
Is break your heart
Is break your heart
Yeah, all I seem to do
Is break your heart
Is break your heart
Is break your heart
So I'll let you go now
Let you go now
Let you go now
